### ============================================
### 一、认证与权限模块 /api/auth
### ============================================

### 1.1 用户注册
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "email": "test@zaran.com",
  "role": "tourist"
}
### 管理员注册
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register/admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
"username": "admin1",
"password": "123456"
}

### 1.2 用户登录（用户名密码）
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 1.2 管理员登录（用户名密码）
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin1",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 1.3 用户登录（手机号）
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "13800138000",
  "password": "123456"
}


### 1.4 用户登录（邮箱）
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test@zaran.com",
  "password": "123456"
}


### 1.5 手机验证码登录（预留）
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login/phone
Content-Type: application/json


### 1.6 微信登录（预留）
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login/wechat
Content-Type: application/json


### 1.7 QQ登录（预留）
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login/qq
Content-Type: application/json


### 1.8 刷新Token（将上方登录返回的refreshToken填入）
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}


### 1.9 忘记密码重置
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/password/reset
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "verifyCode": "123456",
  "newPassword": "654321"
}


### 1.10 退出登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}



### ============================================
### 二、用户管理模块 /api/users
### （需先执行登录，将返回的accessToken填入顶部变量）
### ============================================

### 2.1 获取当前用户信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 2.2 修改个人信息
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "avatar": "https://example.com/avatar.jpg",
  "bio": "专注传统扎染工艺创新设计",
  "professionField": "传统纹样设计"
}


### 2.3 修改密码
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "123456",
  "newPassword": "123456"
}


### 2.4 申请成为设计师
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/apply-designer
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "我有3年传统纹样设计经验，希望通过平台发布作品",
  "portfolioUrl": "https://portfolio.example.com/myworks"
}


### 2.5 查看认证申请列表（传承人/管理员）
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/applications
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 2.6 审核通过设计师申请
### 将 {applicationId} 替换为 2.5 返回的 applicationId
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/applications/1/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reviewerComment": "作品质量合格，同意认证"
}


### 2.7 拒绝设计师申请
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/applications/1/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reviewerComment": "作品不符合要求，请补充后重新申请"
}


### 2.8 查看指定用户主页（公开接口，无需token）
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1


### 2.9 查看用户公开作品（预留）
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1/patterns


### 2.10 查看用户公开草图（预留）
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1/sketches


### 2.11 关注用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/1/follow
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 2.12 取消关注
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/1/follow
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 2.13 未登录访问需认证的接口（应返回401/403）
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/profile



### ============================================
### 四、草图绘制模块 /api/sketches
### （需先执行登录，将返回的accessToken填入顶部变量）
### 测试顺序建议：4.13 → 4.1 → 4.2 → 4.3 → 4.4 → 4.8 → 4.9 → ...
### 将各接口路径中的 {sketchId}/{versionId} 替换为前序接口返回的真实ID
### ============================================

### 4.13 获取草图分类树（公开接口，无需token）
GET {{baseUrl}}/sketches/categories


### 4.14 新增草图分类（仅传承人/管理员；普通游客会返回403）
### 库中无分类时，先用传承人/管理员账号执行此接口，再用返回的 categoryId 跑 4.1
POST {{baseUrl}}/sketches/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "云纹",
  "description": "象征吉祥如意",
  "parentId": null,
  "sortOrder": 1
}


### 4.14b 新增子分类（parentId 填 4.14 返回的 categoryId）
POST {{baseUrl}}/sketches/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "单螺旋",
  "description": "螺旋纹子类",
  "parentId": 1,
  "sortOrder": 1
}


### 4.1 创建新草图
POST {{baseUrl}}/sketches
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "云纹草图v1",
  "width": 1024,
  "height": 1024,
  "categoryId": 1
}


### 4.1b 创建新草图（宽高越界，应返回400）
POST {{baseUrl}}/sketches
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "越界测试",
  "width": 100,
  "height": 5000
}


### 4.2 查询我的草图列表（分页 + 筛选）
GET {{baseUrl}}/sketches?page=1&size=10&keyword=云纹&categoryId=1&isPublic=false&sort=updatedAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 4.2b 查询我的草图列表（含回收站）
GET {{baseUrl}}/sketches?page=1&size=10&includeDeleted=true
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 4.3 获取草图详情
### 将路径中的 1 替换为 4.1 返回的 sketchId
GET {{baseUrl}}/sketches/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 4.4 保存草图（全量更新图层数据）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/sketches/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "云纹草图v3",
  "layersJson": {
    "version": "1.0",
    "canvas": { "width": 1024, "height": 1024 },
    "layers": [
      {
        "id": "layer_1",
        "name": "背景",
        "type": "raster",
        "visible": true,
        "opacity": 1.0,
        "data": "base64_encoded_image_data..."
      },
      {
        "id": "layer_2",
        "name": "线条层",
        "type": "vector",
        "visible": true,
        "paths": [
          { "d": "M10,10 L100,100", "stroke": "#000000", "width": 2 }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  "imageBase64": "data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgo...",
  "isAutoSave": false,
  "tags": ["云纹", "草稿"]
}


### 4.5 设置草图公开/私密
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/sketches/1/visibility
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isPublic": true
}


### 4.8 创建版本快照
POST {{baseUrl}}/sketches/1/versions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "changeDesc": "完成云纹主体绘制",
  "layersJson": {
    "version": "1.0",
    "canvas": { "width": 1024, "height": 1024 },
    "layers": []
  },
  "imageBase64": "data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgo..."
}


### 4.9 获取版本历史（分页）
GET {{baseUrl}}/sketches/1/versions?page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 4.10 获取指定版本详情
### 将第二个 1 替换为 4.8/4.9 返回的 versionId
GET {{baseUrl}}/sketches/1/versions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 4.11 回退到指定版本
POST {{baseUrl}}/sketches/1/versions/1/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 4.12 导入本地图片（multipart/form-data）
### 将 < 后的路径替换为本地真实图片路径（PNG/JPG/SVG，最大20MB）
POST {{baseUrl}}/sketches/1/import
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundaryZaran

------WebKitFormBoundaryZaran
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="asLayer"

true
------WebKitFormBoundaryZaran
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="layerName"

导入图层
------WebKitFormBoundaryZaran
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test.png
------WebKitFormBoundaryZaran--


### 4.6 删除草图（软删除，移入回收站）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/sketches/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 4.7 恢复已删除草图
POST {{baseUrl}}/sketches/1/recover
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 4.14 未登录访问草图列表（应返回401/403）
GET {{baseUrl}}/sketches
